h1. Description

The bundles mbean management bundle exposes a Bundles MBean that can be used with any JMX client (for instance JConsole).

The bundles MBean allows quite the same actions that can be performed using bundle:* commands:
  * list()
  * getStartLevel(bundleId)
  * setStartLevel(bundleId, startLevel)
  * refresh()
  * refresh(bundleId)
  * update(bundleId)
  * update(bundleId, location)
  * resolve()
  * resolve(bundleId)
  * restart(bundleId)
  * install(url)
  * install(url, start)
  * start(bundleId)
  * stop(bundleId)
  * uninstall(bundleId)

